Rating: 4
Fantastic recipe but 45 minutes cooking time is not enough. I doubled the recipe and made the mistake of putting it in a deep dish for cooking. As a result, it took well over an hour to cook and even then it was a bit moist and eggy in the center. In the future I'll use a larger and more shallow dish to ensure it solidifies properly. I used an actual vanilla bean but had to look into a cookbook to find out what to do with it (open the pod with a knife and just scrape out the black material inside -- don't use any of the pod itself). I suspect using a teaspoon of pure vanilla extract would work just as well. Family loved the recipe and we will definitely make it again.

